        <p>theStacc instruments the top and middle of the funnel for you. Our SEO and content engine fills TOFU with organic traffic that compounds monthly, then wires up email nurture and conversion tracking so you can see the real numbers between stages, not just clicks. When something breaks — a landing page conversion rate drops, or a nurture sequence stalls — the audit surfaces it before it costs a month of pipeline.</p>

